\id 1PE - Mpoto Bible Version 
\h 1 Petulu 
\toc1 Baluwa ja kutumbula jaka Petulu 
\toc2 1 Petulu 
\toc3 1 Petu 
\mt2 Baluwa ja kutumbula jaka 
\mt1 Petulu 
\imt1 Ulongulelo 
\ip Baluwa ja kutumbula jaka Mtumi Petulu jakalembakiki na Mtumi Petulu. Petulu akatumbwili kulemba baluwa jaki kwa kulilandila mwene akabhi nane, na akanane bhaakabhili abhalembela. Baluwa jaki jakalandilwi kwa Bhakristo bhokapi bhabhatama “Mundema ngati bhaghene” (1 Petulu 1:1, 1:17; 2:17). Pamaheli jombi abhaloghola bhasomaji bhaki kwa lihina haleli. Bhabhakabhi bhapiti kutama ku inchi patali patali. Kwa kubha baluwa jaki jilengana na baluwa jaka Paulo kwa Bhaefeso kwa ntundu fulani, bhandu bhamaheli bhahobhalili kubha baluwa ja kutumbula jaka Petulu jakalembakiki baada ja baluwa kwa Bhaefeso mu chikahi chechiheghelela chaka cha 65 baada ja kubhelekeka Yesu Kristo. Petulu akalembiki baluwa ajeji akabya mu muchi wa Loma pandu ambapu jombi mwene akapakemiki pa “Babeli,” (Sula 5:13). 
\ip Petulu alongela kubha akajilembiki baluwa ajeji kwa ndandi ja “kubhajeghe mtima na kulandila kubha hachechi nde chihomu cha chakaka chaka Chapanga. Njema kwa ukangamalu mu leniheli, (Sula 5:12).” Kubhi na ulenganu pachilanda ja (1 Petulu 2:11-3:7, Bhaefeso 5:18-6:9, na Bhakolosai 3:18-4:6). Pandu pokapi patatu mu mafungu ghanihagha ghabhoha maelekezu ghokapi ghaghalongalela ntundu familia moipalaki kutama na utii kwa mamulaka ya kiutawala. Kabhete abhajeghe mtima Bhakristo bhahinakalya paghapitali mambu gha kung'ahakika kwa ndandi ujomukelu uheghalile, (Sula 4:1). 
\iot Ghaghabhihomu 
\io1 Petulu alilogho mweni kwa bhasomaji bhaki, (Sula 1:1-2). 
\io1 Kabhete anchengu Chapanga kwa ndandi ja ukengaleku ambau bhokapi bhushiliki, na alandila ndandi ja uchakaka ghonihoghu mu matamu gha ukengaleku wabhu, (Sula 1:3-2:10). 
\io1 Kubhoke panihapa abhapwaghi bhahobhalela ntundu moibhapalaki kutama wichu pundema na ahenge lihengu mambu ghakumu kubhokana na ndomi na nhwanu waki, na mtumwa na bambo waki, (Sula 2:11-4:11). 
\io1 Kabhete Petulu abhajeghe mtima kubha bhahinakalyaje pabhapete mang'ahiku, (Sula 4:12-5:11). 
\io1 Na ajomulela baluwa jaki, (Sula 5:12-14). 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Nepani Petulu, mtumi waka Yesu Kristo: 
\p Nundembe mabhanganya bhahaghulika bhaka Chapanga, mwenga mwemulipechangini na mtama ngati bhagheni mu Ponto, Galatia, Kapodokia, Asia, na Bisinia.  
\v 2 Chapanga Atati akalongulili kummanya mwenga na kunhaghu mwehapa kutumbu pamwande, na akungolwili kwa Roho waki, nahuli muwezaje kumtii Yesu Kristo na kumichakiwa mwahi waki. 
\p Chihomu na lukwali na ijonjukiwa kwino. 
\s1 Lihobhalelu lyome 
\p  
\v 3 Alumbalikaje Chapanga, Atati waka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo! Jombi kwa chiha chaki chikolongwa akatuhengiki tubhelakikaje kwa mala ja kabheli nahuli tupata lihobhalelu lelibhi na womi kwa kuhyoka kwaki Yesu Kristo kuhuma kwa bhabhapotile,  
\v 4 nahuli tupata upwelelu wangakuyonangeka, wanga na uhakau, wanga kujoma, ambau Chapanga atubheki kunani kumahunde kwa ndandi jito.  
\v 5 Nanamu mlendakeka na makili ghaka Chapanga kwa indela ja uhobhalelu mbaka mpata ukengaleku ghoubhi tayali kuhyekuliwa chikahi cha ujomukelo. 
\p  
\v 6 Mhekalya namaa lijambu leniheli, hata ngati sajenu kwa chikahi kichokope, impalika kung'ahakika kwa malengakeku gha ntundu wamaheli.  
\v 7 Malengakeku hagha ghakahikiki nahuli kulangi kubha uhobhelelu winu nde wa chakaka. Hata zahabu jejiweza kuyonangeka najombi jilengakeka kwa moto, bhela uhobhalelu winu nde chindu chikolongwa kupeta zahabu, bhelabhela ipalika jilengakikaje nahuli jikangamalaje. Panihapa ananjopalya sifa na ulumbalilu na utopelu, mu lichobha lela la kuhyekuliwa kwaki Yesu Kristo.  
\v 8 Najombi mumpala hata ngati ngachemumbwene, jombi hata ngati ngachemumbona sajenu, munhobhalela, na kutwelakewa chiheku changakulandika, chechibhi na ulumbalilo,  
\v 9 kwa ndandi njopalela nhupu wa uhobhalelu winu, yani nde, ukengaleku wa roho hino. 
\p  
\v 10 Mu malobhi gha ukengaleku hoghu bhalota bhaka Chapanga bhakalondiki londiki na kuyelabhana yelabhana, ambabu bhakalotiki malobi gha chihomu cheanachunhikila mwenga.  
\v 11 Bhakalondiki kumanya chikahi na pandu papatendakiki lijambu leniheli, chikahi cheakalongili Roho waka Kristo joakabhili mkati jabhu, akalotila panani ja mang'ahiku ghaka Kristo na ulumbalilu ghowijengalyaje.  
\v 12 Chapanga akabhayekuli bhalota bhaki kubha ngachebhakahengiki lihengu kwa nyonjeka jabhu bheni nambu kwa nyonjeka jinu mwenga, pala pabhakapwaghiki malobhi ghani ghampwaghakika sajeju kuhuma kwa bhatumika bhala bhabhuntangazi Malobhi Manyahi kwa makili ghaka Roho Mhuhu joakatumakiki na Chapanga kuhuma kunani kumahunde. Ghanihagha nde mambu ambaghu hata bhatumika bha kunani kumahunde bhapala kughamanya. 
\s1 Ulowakeku wa kutama matamu mahuhu 
\p  
\v 13 Bhela, muikonga ibhunu ya maholalelu ghinu, na kulitawala. Muhobhalya nakanopi chihomu chela cheanampekiwa na Yesu Kristo paibhonikanaje.  
\v 14 Mbya ngati bhana bhabhuntii Chapanga, na ngamwitama kwa kujengalela kabhe matokulelu ghinu mahakau ngati montamila chikahi pamukabhi mwang'ang'a.  
\v 15 Nambu ngati jombi joandohiki mwenga moabhelili mhuhu, mwanganya nanamu mbyaje mwabhahuhu mu matamu ghinu ghokapi.  
\v 16 Maghambu Malembu Mahuhu ghapwagha: “Mbya bhahuhu kwa ndandi Nepani nde mhuhu.” 
\p  
\v 17 Na anakubhili mundobha Atati, jola joantemula kila mundu panga na upendeleu, kulengana na matendu ghaki, njenda kwa choghoi mu chikahi chino cha kutama pani pundema ngati bhaghene.  
\v 18 Kwa ndandi mmanyi kubha mkakombuliwi kuhuma mu matamu ghinu ghangakupalika ambaghu mkapweli kuhuma kwa akahokolu bhino. Ngachemwakombuliwi kwa hindu yeiyonangeka, yani, madini gha feza au zahabu,  
\v 19 nambu kwa mwahi wa samane waka Kristo, ambaju akabhi ngati Mwanambelele jwangakubha na chilema wala dosali.  
\v 20 Jombi akabhi ahaghuliwi na Chapanga mangane ja kubhombakeka ndema, na ahyekuliwi machuwa ghani gha kujomukela kwa ndandi jino.  
\v 21 Kwa indela jaki, mwenga munhobhale Chapanga, joakamuhyohiki kuhuma kwa bhakuwa na kumpeke ulumbalilu, na bhela uhobhalelu winu na lihobhalelu linu libhi kwaka Chapanga. 
\p  
\v 22 Bhela, kwa kubha muigholwi roho hinu kwa kujitii chakaka jela kwa indela jaka Roho nahuli mubhapala bhalongu bhinu kwa upalu wangakubha na undumila kubheli, njendalya kupalana kwa mtima wokapi.  
\v 23 Kwa kubha mbelakiki mala ja kabhele, nga kwa imbeju jejiyonangeka, nambu kwa jela jangakuyonangeka, kwa Lilobhi laka Chapanga lelibi na womi, na lelitamakila hata mileli.  
\v 24 Ngati Malembu Mahuhu moghapwaghila: 
\q1 “Kila mundu nde ngati mahamba, 
\q1 na ulumbalilu waki wokape nde ngati lilobha la muchitengo. 
\q1 Mahamba ghajoma na malobha ghaki ghapuluta. 
\q1  
\v 25 Nambu Lilobhi laka Bambo litamakila mileli.” 
\m Lilobhi leniheli nde Malobhi Manyahi ghala ghamwatangaziwi. 
\c 2  
\s1 Liganga lyomi na litaifa lihuhu 
\p  
\v 1 Bhela, nkotuka mahakau ghokapi, icholi, undumila kubheli, wihu, na kulongalane liyaha ngakwikubha kabhete.  
\v 2 Ngati bhela bhana bhang'eng'a mobhaghatokulela mahibha, na mwanganya nanamu mpalika mughatokulya mahibha gha chakaka gha kiroho ghangakujeghaleka chindu chokapi, nahuli kwa makili ghaki mpata kukola na kukengalewa,  
\v 3 na sajenu mmanyi kubha Bambo nde wambone. 
\p  
\v 4 Bhela, munjendila Bambo, jombi nde liganga la womi lelakanakiki na bhandu, nambu palongi jaka Chapanga nde liganga lelihaghuliki na lelipalika nakanope.  
\v 5 Bhelabhela nanamu munjendila jombi ngati maganga ghaghabhi ghomi, mkachengika na kubha nyumba jaka Roho ambamu anantumakyaje ngati bhapenganyambiku bhahuhu, kwa kubhoha nyambiku ya kiroho ya kunyambiha Chapanga kwa indela jaka Yesu Kristo.  
\v 6 Ndandi Malembu Mahuhu ghapwagha: 
\q1 “Lingalya! Meka liganga likolongwa la kunkeghi mu Sayuni, 
\q1 linganga la luhuli, lihaghulika na lelipalika nakanopi. 
\q1 Mundu joanaanhobhalya jonihoju ngayipowakeki lihamu.” 
\m  
\v 7 Kwinu mwanganya mwemunhobhalela, liganga leniheli nde lelipalika nakanope, nambu kwa bhala bhangakunhobhalela, ngati Malembu Mahuhu moghapwaghila: 
\q1 “Liganga lebhalikaniki bhachenga, 
\q1 sajenu libhi liganga likolongwa la luhuli.” 
\m  
\v 8 Kabhete Malembu Mahuhu ghapwagha: 
\q1 “Liganga leniheli nde liganga la kulikobhando bhandu, 
\q1 na litalaghu la kubhahabhu bhandu.” 
\m Bhandu bhalikobhandola kwa ndandi ngachebhuhobhalela ubholu ghola, bhenibhela nde mobhakabhekakike kutumbu pamwande. 
\p  
\v 9 Nambu mwanganya nde lubheleku luhaghulika, upenganyambiku wa kikolongwa, litaifa lihuhu, bhandu bhaki Chapanga mwene, mwenhaghuliki kutangaza matendu makolongwa ghaka Chapanga joankemiki kuhuma kulwihe, na akunjingi mu unang'anu waki wa kukangacha.  
\v 10 Mwanganya pakutumbula mwakabhi nga litaifa, nambu sajeno mbi bhandu bhaki Chapanga, mwemwabhi ngachemwapatiki chiha, nambu sajeno mpatiki chiha. 
\s1 Bhatumika bhaka Chapanga 
\p  
\v 11 Bhapalu bhango, numpembalake mabhanganya ngati mwagheni na bhabhapeta pani pundema! Nkotukaje matokulelu mahakau gha hyegha ghaghapengana na roho hinu.  
\v 12 Lujendu lwinu pachilanda ja bhandu bhangakunhobhale Chapanga upalika kubha wamboni nakanope, nahuli hata ngati pabhankopunganya kubha muhenga mahakau, bhaweza kumanya matendu ghinu ghambone na bhundumbalya Chapanga mu Lichobha paanahika kutemu ndema. 
\p  
\v 13 Bhela, impalika kubhatii bhatawala bhokapi bha pundema, kwa ndandi jaka Bambo: Utii kwaka nkolongwa joabhi mtawala nkolongwa,  
\v 14 na bhakolongwa ambabhu bhahaghuliki najombi kubhatemula bhahakau na kubhalumbalila bhabhahenga ghamboni.  
\v 15 Kwa ndandi Chapanga apala muweza kughajomola malobhi gha king'ang'a gha bhandu bhanga na malango kwa kutenda matendu ghambone ghamuhenga.  
\v 16 Ntama ngati bhandu bha kulijeka, nambu ngamwitumila kulijeka kwinu kuhiya uhakau, nambu mtama ngati bhatumika bhaka Chapanga.  
\v 17 Mubhatopila bhandu bhokapi, mubhapala bhalongu bhinu bhahobhalela, munjojabya Chapanga, na muntopila nkolongwa. 
\s1 Kung'ahika ngati Kristo 
\p  
\v 18 Mwenga bhatumika, mubhatopila bhakolongwa bhinu kwa utopelu wokape, nga bhala bhabhabhi bhamboni na bhapoli pela, nambu hata bhala bhabhabhi bhakali.  
\v 19 Ndandi ngati anamuhinakila mabhinilu gha mang'ahiku ghangakumpalika kwa ndandi mmanya kubha Chapanga apala bhenibhela, bhela Chapanga anaampengalyaje.  
\v 20 Ndandi bho, anampata nhupu bhole ngati anamuhinakili malapuliko ghampalika kwa ndandi ja mahoku ghinu? Nambu ngati anamuhinakila mang'ahiku kwa kuhenga ghamboni, Chapanga anaampengalyaje.  
\v 21 Ghanihagha nde ghandowakakile; ndandi Kristo mwene akang'ahakike kwa ndandi jino, akandekili ulenganesu, bhela njengalyaje ngati moakahengi jombe.  
\v 22 Jombi ngacheatendiki lihoku, wala lilobhi la upuhi ngacheakapwaghiki lilobhi la upuhe.  
\v 23 Paakatonduliki jombi ngacheakayangiki kwa litondu, paakang'ahakike jombi ngacheakabhohiki malobhi gha kuyoghoha, nambu akaghabhekiki mahobhalelu ghaki kwaka Chapanga, joatemula ngati moipalakila.  
\v 24 Kristo mweni akatotwili mahoku ghitu muhyegha jaki panani ja msalaba, nahuli ngatwihenga mahoku, na kubha tabhomi kwa ndandi ja ghambone. Kwa mabhanga ghaki, mwanganya ndamike.  
\v 25 Mwanganya mkabhili ngati mambeleli ghaghabhili ghahobhiki, nambu sajeno munkelabhukili Mdima na Mlenda wa roho hino. 
\c 3  
\s1 Bhalomi na bhahanu bhabhu 
\p  
\v 1 Bhelabhela akambomba mwentoghuliki, impalika kubhatii bhalomi bhino, nahuli anabhabhi bhalomi bhangakuhobhale Lilobhi laka Chapanga bhapata kuhobhalela kwa lujendu lwinu. Ngakwikubhi na ndandi kwinu mwenga kupwagha lilobhi,  
\v 2 maghambu anabhabhona ntundu lujendu lwinu molubheli lunyahi na lwa kutama ngati moapali Chapanga.  
\v 3 Kulipamba kwinu ngakwikubha kulipamba kwa kunja, yani, kuloka majunju, na kuwata zahabu, na kuwata ingobhu ya mbija yamaheli,  
\v 4 nambu kulipamba kwinu kubya kwa mkati ja mtima wanga kubhonikana, mu mapambu ghangakuyonangeka, yani roho ja upoli na utulivo, leniheli nde lijambu lelipalika nakanopi palongi jaka Chapanga.  
\v 5 Kwa ndandi bhenibhela nde mobhakalipambili akambomba bhahuhu bha mwande, bhabhunhobhalya Chapanga, na kubhatii bhalomi bhabhu.  
\v 6 Ngati bhela Sala moakantii Ibulahimu, akandohiki bambo, nanamu nde akakamwali bhake, pantenda ghambone, wala ngamwijoghopa lijambu lokapi. 
\p  
\v 7 Bhelabhela nanamu bhalomi, mtama nabhu bhahanu bhinu kwa malangu, koni mwakamanya kubha bhombi nde bhazaifu kupeta mwehapa na kubhapeke bhahanu bhinu utopelu, ngati bhapwelelu papamu wa nhupu ja womi ghoampeke Chapanga. Nahuli kulobha kwinu ngakwihibhalika. 
\s1 Kung'ahika kwa ndandi ja kuhenga ghambone 
\p  
\v 8 Ujomukelu mbwagha anana: Mpalika kubha na liholalelu limu, mbyaji mabhandu bha kubhonilana chiha, mpalanaje ngati bhalongu, mbya bhapole na kulihelea.  
\v 9 Ngamwalepa bhandu lihakau kwa lihakau, au litondu kwa litondu, nambu mbya mabhandu mwempengalela, maghambu ghanihagha nde ghandowakakile na Chapanga nahuli mpengalikaje.  
\v 10 Ngati moghapwaghi Malembu Mahuhu: 
\q1 “Joapala kuhekalela matamu, 
\q1 na kubhona machobha ghamboni, 
\q1 aluhibhalakya lulimi lwaki ngailongela mahakau 
\q1 na akotuka kulonge upuhe. 
\q1  
\v 11 Mundu hoju akotuka uhakau, atenda ghamboni, 
\q1 alonda lukwali kwa mtima waki wokapi. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ndandi mihu ghaka Bambo ghabhalingali bhandu bhambone, 
\q1 na makutu ghaki ghajowanela malobhu ghabho, 
\q1 nambu abhalangi chihoghu bhabhahenga mahakau.” 
\p  
\v 13 Bho, nde nane joanaampotika mwenga, ngati ananjomalaki mu kuhenga ghambone?  
\v 14 Nambu hata ngati anaimpaliki kung'ahika kwa ndandi ja kuhenga ghaghapalika kwaka Chapanga, bhela, mpengalike. Ngamwanjoghopa mundu jokapi jola, wala ngamwijetakela kujeghaleka mu choghoi.  
\v 15 Nambu muntopila Kristo Bambo mu mitima jino. Mbya tayali kumuyanga mundu jokapi joanaandalukya panani ja mahobhalelu ghaghabhi mkati jino, nambu muhenga bhenibhela kwa upole na utopelu.  
\v 16 Mkubhaje na zamili jamboni, nahuli pamtonduleka, bhala bhabhapwagha mahakau panani ja luhomu lwinu lyamboni ngati Bhakristo, bhabhona iyone.  
\v 17 Kwa ndandi nde mbanga kung'ahakika kwa ndandi ja kuhenga ghambone, anangati kung'ahakika hoku nde mapalu ghaka Chapanga, kuliku kung'ahakika kwa kuhenga mahakau.  
\v 18 Kwa ndandi Kristo mweni akang'ahakiki kwa ndandi ja mahoku, akapotili punkamu pena na ikayaghanile, mundu jwanga mahoku kwa ndandi ja bhana mahoku, nahuli ampelakaje mwanganya kwaka Chapanga. Akakomakiki kihyegha nambu akatendakiki mwomi kwa uwezu waka Roho Mhuhu,  
\v 19 na kwa matamu ghaki gha kiroho akapiti kubhatangazila roho yela yeikabhi muchifungo.  
\v 20 Bhanihabha nde bhala bhabhakaniki kumtii Chapanga paakabhalendalili kwa uhinakalilu wamaheli chikahi Nuhu paakabhi alenganake safina. Nkati ja safina jela nde bhandu bhachokopi pela, yani bhandu nane pela, bhabhakengaliki mu machi,  
\v 21 na machi ghanihagha ghakabhi ulenganesu wa ubatizo ghounkengele mwanganya sajeno. Ubatizo nga kwa kugholola chihiku chechibhili muhyegha, nambu nde chilanga kwaka Chapanga chechihengakeka mu zamili jinyahi. Unkengalela kwa indela ja kuhyoka kwaka Yesu Kristo,  
\v 22 ambaju akapiti kunani kumahunde na sajenu atami upambala wa kumalelelu wa chiwoku chaka Chapanga, atawala panani ja bhatumika bha kunani kumahunde, na bhabhabhi na lujiniku, na bhabhabhi na makile. 
\c 4  
\s1 Matamu ghahenu 
\p  
\v 1 Bhela kwa ndandi Kristo akang'ahakiki muhyegha jake, na mwanganya nanamu mbya na liholalelu lelele ngati jombi, maghambu jombi joang'ahakike muhyegha alekini na mahoku.  
\v 2 Kutumbu sajeno matamu ghaghahighali kutama pani pundema impalika kutama ngati moapali Chapanga, wala nga kwa matokulelu ghinu mahakau gha kimundu.  
\v 3 Maghambu pamwande mkabhi na chikahi chilachu cha kuhenga mambu ghabhahenga bhandu bhangakummanya Chapanga. Mkatami kwa kuhenga ukemi, matokulelu mahakau, kulobhela uwembi, uwangalalu wa kulobhela uwembi nakanope, na kulobhela na kuhenga mambu mahakau, na kujojabhela imong'umong'u.  
\v 4 Sajenu, bhandu bhangakummanya Chapanga habha bhunkangacha pabhabhona kubha ngachendombana nabhu kabhete mu kuhenga mahakau ghaghapetali hagha, na bhela bhatenda kuntondola.  
\v 5 Nambu anabhapalika kumuyanga Chapanga panani ja mambu ghabhu ghabhahengike, chikahi Chapanga paabhatemu bhabhabhi bhomi na bhabhapotile.  
\v 6 Nde ndandi hata Malobhi Manyahi ghakatangizwi hata kwa bhandu bhala bhabhapotile, nahuli baada ja kutemuliwa mu matamu ghabhu gha kihyegha ngati bhandu bhange, bhatamaje kwa ndandi jaka Chapanga kwa indela jaka Roho Mhuhu. 
\s1 Mtumika wambone wa nhupu yaka Chapanga 
\p  
\v 7 Ujomukelu wa mambu ghokape uheghalile, bhela, mlilingalyaje na mkeshaje kwa kundobha Chapanga.  
\v 8 Nakanopi ja ghanihagha ghokapi mpalanaje mabheti kwa mabheti, maghambu upalu uyekale mahoku ghamahele.  
\v 9 Nkalibishanaje kwa upalu mabheni kwa mabheni panga na kung'ong'uteka.  
\v 10 Kila jumu apalika kutumila nhupu jeapekiwi na Chapanga kwa nyonjeka ja bhandu bhange, ngati njemalela wambone wa chihomu patalipatali yaka Chapanga.  
\v 11 Mundu jokapi joatangaza, apalika atangaza malobhi ghaka Chapanga; joatumika apalika utumakya kwa makili ghaapekewa na Chapanga, nahuli Chapanga alumbalikaje kupetela Yesu Kristo kwa ghokapi. Ulumbalilu na uweza ubhi najombi mileli na mileli. Amina. 
\s1 Kung'ahika kwa kunhobhale Kristo 
\p  
\v 12 Bhapalu bhangu, ngamwikangacha panani ja malengakeku makolongwa ghamughapata, kwa ndandi mambu ghaghumpata nga maghene.  
\v 13 Nambu mhekalyaje maghambu mkang'ahakiki ngati Kristo moakang'ahakike nahuli pawiyekuliwa ulumbalilu waki muhekalya nakanope.  
\v 14 Muhekalyaje ngati anabhuntondola kwa ndandi ja kunjengale Kristo, maghambu Roho wa ulumbalilu joabhi Roho waka Chapanga atama na mwehapa.  
\v 15 Ngati mundu jokapi anaang'ahika, ngaying'ahika kwa ndandi jombi nde mkoma bhandu, mwihi, mundu joahenga mahakau au joajingalila mambu gha bhandu bhange.  
\v 16 Nambu anangati mundu ang'ahika maghambu anhobhale Kristo, bhela, ngayibhona iyone, nambu andumbalya Chapanga, kwa kulowakeka kwa lihina laka Kristo. 
\p  
\v 17 Kwa ndandi chikahi cha utemulo chihikike na utemulu hoghu utumbu na bhandu bhaka Chapanga. Bhela anangati utemulu hoghu utumbu kwitu tepani, bho, anakubya bhole kwa bhandu bhala bhangakuhobhalela Malobhi Manyahi ghaka Chapanga?  
\v 18 Ngati Malembu Mahuhu moghapwaghila: 
\q1 “Ngati anakunonopa kwaka mundu joahenga ngati moapali Chapanga kukengalewa, 
\q1 bho, anakubya bhole kwaka mundu jwangakumtii Chapanga na mwana mahoku?” 
\m  
\v 19 Bhela bhala bhabhang'ahika ngati moapali Chapanga, bhajendalya kuhenga matendu ghambone na kulibheka bheni kwaka Jobhabhombike ambaju nde ndongwana nakanope. 
\c 5  
\s1 Lipogha laka Chapanga 
\p  
\v 1 Nepani nde mzee pachilanda jinu mwehapa mabhazee bhajango, nepani ambaju nakalandili mang'ahiku ghaka Kristo, na mshilika wa ulumbalilu ghowiyekuliwaje panakatae.  
\v 2 Nundobha nakanope, mlighohaje lipogha laka Chapanga lelibhi kwino, na kulijemalela, nga kwa kujomalakewa, nambu kwa kupala mabhene ngati moapali Chapanga. Muhengaje lihengu leniheli nga kwa kutokule mbija, nambu kwa mtima winu wokapi.  
\v 3 Ngamubhatawala kwa makile bhanihabha bhabhabhekakiki pahi ja ujemalelu winu, nambu mbya ulenganesu kwa lipogha lenihele.  
\v 4 Na chikahi Mdima Nkolongwa paanaapitalyaje, mwehapa ananjopalya litaji la ulumbalilu langakuhoa unyahi waki. 
\p  
\v 5 Bhelabhela nanamu akakombo impalika kubhatii bhazee. Mabhokapi impalika kuliheleya na kutumakilana, maghambu Malembu Mahuhu ghapwagha: “Chapanga abhapenga bhabhalibhona, nambu abhapeke chihomu bhabhaliheleya.”  
\v 6 Bhela muliheliaje pahi ja chiwoku chechibhi na makile chaka Chapanga, nahuli ankwehaje mu chikahi chechipalika.  
\v 7 Muntweka matatizu ghinu ghokapi, maghambu jombi angoha kwa mambu ghinu ghokapi. 
\p  
\v 8 Mlilendaje na mbya mihu! Maghambu adui winu Shetani, ayongolota yongolota ngati lihimba lelinguluma, likalonda mundu wa kummemena.  
\v 9 Njemakakya lukwale mu uhubhalelo na mumpenga Shetani, koni mkamanya kubha bhalongu bhahobhalela bhajinu pundema pokapi bhapata mang'ahiku ghaghagha.  
\v 10 Nambu ananjomwi kung'ahakika kwa chikahi kichokope, Chapanga wa chihomu chokapi na ambaju andoha mwenga kujingila mu ulumbalilu waki wa mileli mu kulombana na Kristo Yesu, jombi mweni anaantenda kubha bhomi kabhete na kumpeke ukangamalu na makili, na kumpeke luhuli lwa chakaka.  
\v 11 Uweza ubhi na jombe hata mileli na mileli! Amina. 
\s1 Malamukilu gha kujomulela 
\p  
\v 12 Nundembi baluwa jenjenu jijipi kwa kujangatiwa na Silivano, ndongu ambaju nummanyi na nunhobhalela. Mbala kunjeghe mtima na kulandila kubha lijambu lendenu nde chihomu cha chakaka chaka Chapanga. Njendalya kutamakila mu chihomu cheniheche. 
\p  
\v 13 Lipogha la bhahobhalela bhajinu bhabhahaghuliki papamu na mwehapa bhabhatama ku Babeli bhundamukila. Bhelabhela Mako ambaju nde mwana wangu mu uhobhalelu andamukila.  
\v 14 Ndamukanya kwa upalu wa Kikristo. 
\p Lukwali lukubhaje na mwehapa mabhokapi mwembili muka Kristo. Amina.